# TONY-PLUGS Project Hints
# This file is read by all OpenCode instances working on this project.

## Project Type
JUCE-based VST plugin (C++) with React/TypeScript design system prototype.

## Architecture
- `/src/` — React/Vite TypeScript prototype (design system, interaction testing)
- `/juce/` — Production JUCE C++ plugin code
- `/docs/` — Documentation, style guides, agent roster
- `/.opencode/` — Agent configurations
- `/.viking/` — Shared memory, preferences, skills

## Key Rules
1. NO AAX format — only VST3, AU, Standalone
2. NO Projucer — pure CMake builds
3. C++17 minimum for JUCE code
4. Visual style = "La Linea" / Linus på linjen (thick white lines, bold backgrounds)
5. Colors: #1E5AA8 (blue), #2E8B57 (green), #F4D03F (yellow), white lines, black borders
6. Knob thickness: 12px. Waveform thickness: 6px. Always rounded caps.
7. Test interaction patterns in TypeScript FIRST, then port to JUCE C++
8. Audio thread: NO memory allocation, NO mutexes, NO UI calls
9. Parameters via AudioProcessorValueTreeState only
10. Animation via juce::Timer at 30-60fps

## File References
- Style guide: docs/STYLE_GUIDE.md
- Agent roles: docs/AGENTS.md
- Skills catalog: docs/SKILLS.md
- Viking preferences: .viking/preferences/linus-style.yaml

## Build
```bash
# React prototype
npm install && npm run dev

# JUCE plugin
cd juce && mkdir -p build && cd build
cmake .. -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release
cmake --build . --parallel
```
